item.description:
Book Review: The Willpower Instinct by Kelly McGonigal - CharlesNgo.com

The Willpower Instinct by Kelly McGonigal. If there's one thing we could all use more of, it's self-control. Think about the most successful people you know vs. the ones that aren't. What's the main difference? It's their self-control and their ability to continuously do the right actions.
